n                <li>Establish automated database pool monitoring and alerting thresholds. Create alerts for pool exhaustion conditions at 75% and 90% capacity to enable faster detection and response to similar incidents in the future.</li>\n            </ol>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null,"userModified":false},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"a5ab7337-584b-4797-95b7-53de354b7bdd","userType":"external","entrypoint":"sdk-cli","cwd":"/Users/boeschj/Documents/GitHub/parchment/bench/.runs/2026-07-12T07-53-15-666Z/incident-report/html/rep-1","sessionId":"dbb514ed-3bcd-4378-b3bc-8b0026dd44fa","version":"2.1.207","gitBranch":"main"}
